een}} |6,065\n|{{Party shading/Green}} |3.18%\n|\n|-\n|2016\n|[[United States House of Representatives|U.S. House of Representatives]]\n|[[General election (U.S.)|General]]\n|\n|{{Party shading/Republican}} |'''Bill Johnson'''\n|{{Party shading/Republican}} |[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|{{Party shading/Republican}} |213,975\n|{{Party shading/Republican}} |70.68%\n|\n|{{Party shading/Democratic}} |Mike Lorentz\n|{{Party shading/Democratic}} |[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|{{Party shading/Democratic}} |88,780\n|{{Party shading/Democratic}} |29.32%\n|\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://billjohnson.house.gov/ Congressman Bill Johnson] official U.S. House site\n* [http://www.billjohnsonleads.com/ Bill Johnson for Congress]\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Ohio/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Bill_Johnson_%5BR-06%5D|Bill Johnson}}\n* {{C-SPAN|billjohnson07}}\n{{CongLinks | congbio = J000292 | ballot = Bill_Johnson_(Ohio) | nndb = 848/000265053 | votesmart = 120649 | govtrack = 412460 | opencong = 412460 | rollcall = 32942 | politifact = bill-johnson | fec = H0OH06189 | opensecrets = N00032088 | assets = bill-johnson | legistorm = 2781/Rep_Bill_Johnson_OH.html | followthemoney = | ontheissues = OH/Bill_Johnson.htm | congress = bill-johnson/2046 | worldcat = | c-span = billjohnson07 | rose = | imdb = | bloomberg = | nyt = | wsj = | washpo = gIQAHF5YKP }}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n| state=Ohio\n| district=6\n|before=[[Charlie Wilson (Ohio politician)|Charlie Wilson]]\n|after=Incumbent|years=January 3, 2011 \u2013 present}}\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Robert Hurt (Virginia politician)|Robert Hurt]]<br><small>R-[[Virginia]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=''[[List of current members of the United States House of Representatives by seniority|United States Representatives by seniority]]''|years=260th}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[William R. Keating|Bill Keating]]<b